WEBVTT

00:05:29.420 --> 00:05:32.000
My knees and my ankles wouldn't bend

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:36.710
and at one point I traumatized
all the skiers on the chair lift

00:05:36.710 --> 00:05:41.070
when I fell and my legs,

00:05:41.070 --> 00:05:43.000
still attached to my snowboard —

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:47.000
(Laughter) —

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:50.000
went flying down the mountain,

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:53.000
and I was on top of the mountain still.

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:55.000
I was so shocked,

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:59.308
I was just as shocked as everybody else,
and I was so discouraged,

00:05:59.308 --> 00:06:03.000
but I knew that if I could find the right pair of feet